  <description>
  <p>A simple application that installs and updates the Adwaita-for-Steam skin.</p>
  <p>Install Directions:</p>
  <ol>
    <li>Install skin via app</li>
    <li>Restart Steam if running</li>
  </ol>
  <p>
    On startup new releases will automatically be downloaded and display a notification.
    Simply reinstall the skin and restart Steam to update.
  </p>
  <p>Note: In order to get rounded corners on Steam, you will need to use the "Rounded Window Corners" gnome extension.</p>
  </description>

